name: Anabelle Geller
description: Working with Karen Whitt, from the Figueroa Group, on the purchase of my first house in Orlando was a very positive and pleasant experience. I moved from NY to Orlando and she kept me informed every step of the process. She was not only professional, knowledgeable and responsive but so easy to work with. I am pleased and grateful for all her advice and information about Orlando, that I am working with her again on getting a property for my son, and will continue to call on her for any future property deals. Less.
